    "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nSpark 3.4+ adds a configuration flag for their ORC vectorized writer called `spark.sql.orc.columnarWriterBatchSize` (it defaults to 1024). The RAPIDS Accelerator should look into also add an equivalent flag for its ORC writer (such as `spark.rapids.sql.writer.batchSizeRows`), and default its value as well.  It could also be a soft limit like the reader parameters.\r\n\r\nSpark PR commit: https://github.com/apache/spark/commit/a9b2a2e92b ",
